title: 317A.901 SERVICE OF PROCESS ON CORPORATION.
text:
A process, notice, or demand required or permitted by law to be served upon a corporation may be served upon the registered agent, if any, of the corporation named in the articles, upon an officer of the corporation, or upon the secretary of state as provided in section 5.25.
